snippet.title: BRUTALISTIKA - Trailer 12/24
snippet.description:
BRUTALISTIKA is an immersive and contemplative experience. In this walking simulator, explore mysterious and intriguing liminal spaces with neo-brutalist architecture at your own pace, filled with serene pools and interactive artworks that invite you to be aware of your emotions.

BRUTALISTIKA will soon be released on steam ! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3372000/BRUTALISTIKA/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=first-page-dec-2024&utm_medium=social&
